{"TopicId":155506,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"Would This Work?","CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T18:55:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T18:55:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo I had an idea recently. First, you build a ring in low orbit, but locked to the planet by towers. Secondly, you run a smaller ring with magnets attached around at orbital velocity inside a copper-wire-lined enclosure. Wouldn\u0027t this generate a crapton of power for basically no operating cost beyond, y\u0027know, space rings and elevators?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:11:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe energy has to come from somewhere. Your magnet-studded ring would quickly stop as its kinetic energy is converted to electrical energy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darnok","CreatedById":85708,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:17:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285066\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe energy has to come from somewhere. Your magnet-studded ring would quickly stop as its kinetic energy is converted to electrical energy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism itself is form of energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:19:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933033\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285464\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285708\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Darnok\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Darnok said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism itself is form of energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd what mechanism do you propose that would extract it / convert to something that can be turned into something useful?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-24T19:20:18Z\u0022 title=\u002201/24/2017 07:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 24, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Shpaget\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:21:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285585\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002245577\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Shpaget\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Shpaget said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd what mechanism do you propose that would extract it / convert to something that can be turned into something useful?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a big generator...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933029\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285066\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe energy has to come from somewhere. Your magnet-studded ring would quickly stop as its kinetic energy is converted to electrical energy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo. Gravity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:22:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933036\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285663\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a big generator...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is spinning this generator?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:23:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:24:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity pulls down, not sideways.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:25:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo put two really heavy weights on either end\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:27:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat end? It\u0027s a ring.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity always pulls towards the center of the planet (and the ring).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:27:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nahh i see.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"radonek","CreatedById":84077,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:28:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933040\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285788\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInertia.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darnok","CreatedById":85708,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:33:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933034\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285585\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002245577\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Shpaget\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Shpaget said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd what mechanism do you propose that would extract it / convert to something that can be turned into something useful?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is answer worth Nobel prize \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Shpaget","CreatedById":45577,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:35:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933056\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485286425\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285708\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Darnok\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Darnok said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat is answer worth Nobel prize \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan\u0027t blame me for trying to nick it, can you? XD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-24T19:35:25Z\u0022 title=\u002201/24/2017 07:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 24, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Shpaget\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mikki","CreatedById":137508,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T19:42:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe, this idea is many years old. \u0022Harnessing a current from\u00A0a cable around the equator\u0022. If this\u00A0works...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrbitalBuzzsaw","CreatedById":158329,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T20:54:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933072\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485286977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022137508\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Mikki\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Mikki said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe, this idea is many years old. \u0022Harnessing a current from\u00A0a cable around the equator\u0022. If this\u00A0works...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_rolleyes.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:rolleyes:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"p1t1o","CreatedById":74091,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T12:26:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933033\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285464\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285708\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Darnok\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, Darnok said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism itself is form of energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOof. Oh no, no nooo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou cannot extract energy from a magnet without first putting energy in. A magnetic field is not a source of energy although you can use it to store energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThink of a\u00A0magnetic field as a spring. You cannot extract energy from a spring, its just a piece of metal. If you squeeze it though, you are putting energy in, which you can store in the spring and release later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933040\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285788\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n16 hours ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh jeeze what is happening?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts the same with gravity although because there is no repulsion force its a little different. Yes you can drop something into a gravity well and see energy come from that. But you can only do it once, if you dont add energy to the system, the object you drop will stay at the bottom of the gravity well forever. You\u0027re not really extracting energy from gravity, you are extracting it from the relationship between two seperated masses. You can add and subtract energy from that system, but you cant extract energy from a single mass\u0027s gravity well. Dont go banging on about collapsing the mass into its own schwartzchild radius, that is just an extension of the stored energy situation explained just above.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T12:48:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd if place a lot of rings one above another, it will be a Dyson sphere.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485347196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933033\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285464\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285708\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Darnok\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Darnok said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism itself is form of energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOof. Oh no, no nooo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485347196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933040\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485285788\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158329\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrbitalBuzzsaw\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, OrbitalBuzzsaw said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGravity\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh jeeze what is happening?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMmmmm... The Love?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-25T12:51:15Z\u0022 title=\u002201/25/2017 12:51  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 25, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T16:19:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/74091-p1t1o/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002274091\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/74091-p1t1o/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@p1t1o\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Thanks for explaining it much better than I\u00A0could.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Original Post(er). The first post in a thread, or the person who posted it.\u0022\u003EOP\u003C/abbr\u003E: The bottom line is that your concept violates the law of conservation of energy. Never mind the engineering hurdles of building such a thing, it would soon stop as you extract energy from it. The energy\u00A0\u003Cstrong\u003Ehas\u003C/strong\u003E\u00A0to come from somewhere, and magnetism and/or gravity won\u0027t provide it, they\u00A0just facilitates the conversion.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jovus","CreatedById":117163,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T17:29:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism does no work. It is not a form of energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMagnetism is a force. But again, a force incapable of doing work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTo more fully answer the question: no, this would not work, and yes-maybe-kind-of this would work.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSetting aside deformations from other celestial bodies for a moment, the Earth\u0027s magnetic field rotates with the Earth (more or less; we\u0027re also ignoring the liquidity of the mantle).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you put a ring up there in orbit not connected with the Earth, the ring would move through Earth\u0027s magnetic field and a current would flow around the ring. However, if you tapped that current (and you would have to, to keep the ring from melting), the ring would slow to a stop and fall out of the sky, because energy must come from somewhere, and the energy creating the current is the energy of orbit. To counteract this, you\u0027d have to use station-keeping fuel. So you\u0027d ultimately be finding an extremely inefficient and expensive way to trade rocket fuel for electricity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you attached the ring via a long pylon to the ground, however, then the ring would be \u0027orbiting\u0027 the Earth with the same period as the Earthly rotation. Therefore it would not move relative to the Earth\u0027s magnetic field, and therefore it would not induce a current.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow, that last bit is a bit oversimplified. The magnetic field of the Earth doesn\u0027t \u003Cem\u003Equite\u003C/em\u003E move exactly with Earth\u0027s rotation, due to many factors (the liquidity of the Earth, deformations from celestial bodies and events, etc.) So you probably would be able to induce some current, especially with a very long ring (which you have). At that point, instead you\u0027d be slowing the rotation of the Earth (albeit minutely, because she\u0027s a big\u0027un).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darnok","CreatedById":85708,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T18:54:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933860\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485347196\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002274091\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022p1t1o\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, p1t1o said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOof. Oh no, no nooo.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou cannot extract energy from a magnet without first putting energy in. A magnetic field is not a source of energy although you can use it to store energy.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThink of a\u00A0magnetic field as a spring. You cannot extract energy from a spring, its just a piece of metal. If you squeeze it though, you are putting energy in, which you can store in the spring and release later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou are wrong... take for example neodymium, this is your spring. If you put energy in it you add magnetic capabilities to this piece of metal. Now you have squeezed spring ready to make work (release energy).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKey thing is to develop mechanism able to drain energy stored in neodymium and of course you can not drain more energy than you stored \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T19:14:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222934268\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485370491\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002285708\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Darnok\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 minutes ago, Darnok said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you put energy in it you add magnetic capabilities to this piece of metal.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust orienting its atoms, not storing an energy.\u003Cbr\u003E\nMaking its structure to betray the Chaos and turn to the Order.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darnok","CreatedById":85708,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T19:27:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222934293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485371683\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust orienting its atoms, not storing an energy.\u003Cbr\u003E\nMaking its structure to betray the Chaos and turn to the Order.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, which means if you would be able to build device that would disorienting atoms of neodymium you should in result also get fraction of energy used in process of manufacturing neodymium magnet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T19:28:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, you should just apply more energy (say, heat) to make them reorient again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Darnok","CreatedById":85708,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T19:37:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222934313\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022155506\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485372531\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo, you should just apply more energy (say, heat) to make them reorient again.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want to lose all stored energy, yes, but we don\u0027t want to lose it, we want to get it back \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}